headline: Barclays Lowers Price Target on The Mosaic Company (MOS) to $31, Maintains Overweight Rating
summary: The Mosaic Company (NYSE:MOS) is among the 11 Most Oversold S&P 500 Stocks Heading into 2026. On December 9, Barclays lowered its price target on the stock to $31 from $35, while keeping an Overweight rating on the shares. This follows the firm’s November reduction of its target price on the stock to $35 from […]
